      <title>利洁时的季度销售额和前景令投资者失望</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/reckitt-posts-drop-fourth-quarter-like-for-like-net-revenue-2024-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[消费品集团利洁时 (Reckitt) 周三未能达到第四季度同比净销售额预期，因一些投资者批评该公司 2024 年销售和盈利前景“模糊”，该公司股价下跌 10%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/reckitt-posts-drop-fourth-quarter-like-for-like-net-revenue-2024-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 07:19:13 GMT</pubDate>
